        '{{strong:The Accessories & Swag:}} If an accessory or non-tobacco item does not meet your expectations, unused items in their original, pristine packaging may be returned within 3 days of delivery. Buyers are responsible for return shipping costs unless the incorrect item was sent by us.',
      ],
    ],
  },
  {
