        '{{strong:Trusted Partners:}} We utilize secure, industry-leading platforms and payment gateways to handle your transactions. By purchasing from us, you also agree to their secure data handling practices.',
        '{{strong:Communication:}} By providing your email address, you agree to receive order updates and occasional insights into new releases. You may opt out of marketing communications at any time.',
      ],
    ],
  },
  {
    heading: '6. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY',
    blocks: [
      'Everything displayed on this website, including the Mariposa name, logo, images, tasting notes, brand stories, and custom design elements, is protected under intellectual property laws. You may not copy, reproduce, resell, or exploit any portion of our content or assets without our express, written consent.',
    ],
  },
  {
    heading: '7. THIRD-PARTY TOOLS',
    blocks: [
      'We rely on third-party infrastructure (such as e-commerce platforms and secure payment processors) to keep our digital lounge running seamlessly. We are not responsible for third-party service interruptions, technical downtime, or the policies of external websites linked from our pages.',
